</reflist>
</incoming>
<name>
<val>is supported special command</val>
</name>
<note>
<val>	General:
	CLEAR - for clearing the stack 
	TOP - get top element
	DUP - duplicate top element	
	SWAP - swap top 2 elements
	EXIT - quit the program

	Math:
	SIN - sinus of top number
	COS - cosine of top number
	EXP - e powered by top number
	POW - power operation of top 2 numbers</val>
</note>
<outgoing>
<reflist>
<ref refid="9c35ee36-37b7-11f1-9394-50ebf6e4fe33"/>
</reflist>
</outgoing>
